Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.67,0:00:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.83,0:01:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.24,0:01:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we talk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.08,0:01:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We must break through the ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.50,0:01:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The men are hungry and exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.01,0:01:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We cannot keep up this\Npace without consequence.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.24,0:01:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen up, men!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.87,0:01:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The more we delay the labor,\Nthe firmer the grasp of the ice will become.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.03,0:01:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The work continues.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.29,0:01:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Rotate each group.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.73,0:01:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, with respect,\Nthe men need assurances.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.94,0:01:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Assurances?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.04,0:01:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that we will head back\Nto St. Petersburg once we free the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.88,0:01:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't think we'll be seaworthy\Nfor long and they want to know--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.66,0:01:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.88,0:01:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's neither your place, nor the officer here to think anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.96,0:01:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We signed up for a mission and\Nwe'll see it to completion.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.63,0:02:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We will reach the North Pole.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.04,0:02:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it understood?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.81,0:02:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,An explosion, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.46,0:02:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,About two miles away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.55,0:02:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Get the men.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.70,0:03:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The sled dogs are unharmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.18,0:03:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Then where does all this blood come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.15,0:03:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Over here, Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.31,0:03:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,A wounded man, he's lost a lot of blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.00,0:03:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Wound to the shoulder.\NHis leg is broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.07,0:03:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Bear attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.75,0:03:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think so, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.90,0:03:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Larsen, help me with his boot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.55,0:03:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,A prosthetic leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.04,0:03:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Put him on the board.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.99,0:03:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry to the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.77,0:04:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Larsen, that thing is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.87,0:04:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready the rifles!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.49,0:04:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,On my command.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.61,0:04:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Aim!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.79,0:04:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.20,0:04:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.46,0:04:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,All to the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.70,0:05:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the man we brought onboard?!\NWhere?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.87,0:05:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that thing?\NWhat does it want?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.08,0:05:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The Blunderbuss!\NLarsen, get the Blunderbuss!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.74,0:06:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I killed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.39,0:06:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I killed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.95,0:06:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's still alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.05,0:06:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ladder!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.23,0:06:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Pull up the ladder!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.79,0:07:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,How many shots are left?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.57,0:07:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,One, but it can't kill it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.67,0:07:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.49,0:07:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not aiming for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.70,0:10:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Come down, your father is arriving.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.95,0:10:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here, Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.91,0:10:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.83,0:15:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Three.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.11,0:15:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Two.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.44,0:15:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,One.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.18,0:15:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.08,0:15:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.13,0:36:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Help him.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.31,0:36:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Help him!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.17,0:36:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You better come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.84,0:36:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.23,0:36:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, the watchman saw him.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.76,0:36:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Circling the ship in the mist.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.55,0:36:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We all saw him drown.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.19,0:36:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, the men are terrified.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.02,0:37:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,They think that man should be surrendered\Nto the ice and be done with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.33,0:37:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He's under my protection, and the protection of the Crown!
Dialogue: 0,2:18:47.31,2:18:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Weapons down.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:49.07,2:18:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,- Put them down!\N- I am responsible for my men.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:52.45,2:18:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,He can leave.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:28.58,2:20:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We're free!\NWe're free!
Dialogue: 0,2:20:32.49,2:20:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain, what are your orders?
Dialogue: 0,2:20:36.19,2:20:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Man the sails.\NTurn around.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:38.73,2:20:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to tell the men?
Dialogue: 0,2:20:40.70,2:20:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Men!
Dialogue: 0,2:20:42.99,2:20:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We're sailing home!
Dialogue: 0,2:20:44.80,2:20:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We're sailing home!
